    <div class="container">
        <div class="product">
            <h2>Our Product</h2>
            <img src="img/OurProduct.png" alt="Product Image">
            <p><strong>Welcome to the future of employee scheduling with Employee Smart Roster.</strong> Our innovative platform is designed to streamline workforce management, making it easier for businesses of all sizes to create, manage, and optimize employee schedules.</p>

            <p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Automated Scheduling:</strong> Leverage powerful algorithms to automatically generate optimal schedules based on employee availability, skills, and business needs.</li>
                <li><strong>Real-Time Updates:</strong> Instantly update and communicate schedule changes to your team, ensuring everyone is always in the loop.</li>
                <li><strong>Employee Self-Service:</strong> Empower your employees with self-service features, allowing them to request time off, swap shifts, and view their schedules anytime, anywhere.</li>
                <li><strong>Compliance and Reporting:</strong> Stay compliant with labor laws and regulations with built-in compliance checks and detailed reporting features.</li>           
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Increased Efficiency:</strong> Save time and reduce errors with automated scheduling, allowing managers to focus on more strategic tasks.</li>
                <li><strong>Enhanced Flexibility:</strong> Accommodate last-minute changes and employee preferences effortlessly, improving overall job satisfaction.</li>
                <li><strong>Better Insights:</strong> Gain valuable insights into workforce trends and performance with comprehensive analytics and reporting tools.</li>
                <li><strong>Cost Savings:</strong> Optimize labor costs by ensuring the right number of staff are scheduled at the right times, reducing overtime and understaffing issues.</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Join the growing number of businesses transforming their scheduling processes with Employee Smart Roster. Experience the future of workforce management today!</p>
